high_descs: turn left, walk to the tub
grab the dirty clothes by the tub
turn left, walk to the tub
put the clothes in the sink
turn around, walk to the sink on the right
open the right door of the cabinet under the sink, take the cloth out, close the cabinet
turn right, walk to the tub
put the cloth in the tub
anns.task_desc: put two cloth in the tub

high_descs: Turn left and walk across the room to face the sink.
pick up the tissue on the counter.
Turn left and take a step and turn right to face the sink.
Put the tissue in the sink
Turn around and take a step, then turn right to face another sink.
Open the cabinet and take out the tissue in the cabinet and then close the cabinet.
Turn around and take a step and then turn left and walk to the sink.
Place the tissue into the sink.
anns.task_desc: To place two tissues into the sink.

high_descs: Turn around to your left and walk towards the sink counter
Pick up the cloth on the right side corner of the tub
Turn to your left then walk few step turn to right
Put the cloth in the tub beside the soap
Turn around to your left head to the cabinet under the sink
Open the cabinet, pick up a cloth inside then close the cabinet
Turn around to your right head back to the tub
Drop the cloth in the tub beside the other cloth
anns.task_desc: Put two cloth in the tub

high_descs: Turn and go to the right side of the tub.
Pick up the wash rag that is on the right side of the tub.
With the wash rag in hand turn and go to the center of the tub.
Place the wash rag in the center of the tub.
Turn and go to the sink.
Open the cabinet on the right under the sink. Grab the wash rag. Shut the cabinet door.
Turn and go to the center of the bath tub with the wash rag.
Place the wash rag to the left of the wash rag that is already in the tub.
anns.task_desc: Put wash rags in the tub.

high_descs: Turn left and walk over to the tub.
Pick up the white rag that is on the counter to the right of the tub.
Turn left and begin walking across the room, then turn right to face the tub.
Place the white rag into the tub to the left of the bar of soap that is already in there.
Turn around and begin walking across the room, then hang a right and walk up to the rightmost sink faucet.
Open the rightmost cabinet door below the sink and remove the white rag inside, then close the door.
Turn around and begin walking across the room, then hang a left and walk up to the tub.
Place the white rag in the tub to the left of the rag that is already in there.
anns.task_desc: Move two white rags into the tub.
